Technologies Used:
Language: Python

Libraries: TensorFlow, Keras, NumPy, Matplotlib, OpenCV

Model: MobileNetV2 (Transfer Learning)

Tool (Optional): Streamlit for user interface

Dataset: TrashNet or Garbage Classification Dataset from Kaggle

